reviews.review_text:
Best energy on Eyes of the World. I have been looking for this show for years. At 6.18 to 6.35 Jerry is playing lead and at this point he comes up with the power of Jerry. 
    The band accelerates at this point and at the same time you can hear the auduance accelerate exactly at the at the same time. 
    This is one of the times where Garcia efects the band and the audiance when we all were in the same like minded space in a show,  . 
    This is the magic they have given me 100's of times but is is exceptional. Please listen and let me know if any real deadheads can feel it.   It literly brings tears to my eyes.
